16
00:02:41,430 --> 00:02:41,960
Fine.

17
00:02:42,190 --> 00:02:43,050
Keep sleeping.

18
00:02:43,560 --> 00:02:44,820
You won't get to eat it.

19
00:03:26,180 --> 00:03:27,790
[Lu Shangxia, Raccoon Dog Demon]

20
00:03:28,710 --> 00:03:30,110
Who? Who was that? Who...

21
00:03:31,079 --> 00:03:31,810
Pretending.

22
00:03:32,240 --> 00:03:33,000
Still pretending with me?

23
00:03:33,000 --> 00:03:33,560
I'm not.

24
00:03:33,560 --> 00:03:34,290
Give it to me!

25
00:03:34,560 --> 00:03:35,090
Alright.

26
00:03:36,280 --> 00:03:37,079
Give you what?

27
00:03:38,680 --> 00:03:40,470
Give it to me!

28
00:03:49,560 --> 00:03:50,470
You're the fastest

29
00:03:50,470 --> 00:03:52,329
but the dumbest raccoon dog demon

30
00:03:52,400 --> 00:03:53,840
in your clan,

31
00:03:53,960 --> 00:03:54,590
Lu Qiba.

32
00:03:55,190 --> 00:03:56,430
The other one is your brother,

33
00:03:56,430 --> 00:03:58,030
who is even dumber than you:

34
00:03:58,430 --> 00:03:59,240
Lu Shangxia.

35
00:04:00,710 --> 00:04:01,590
I heard that you two

36
00:04:01,590 --> 00:04:03,990
couldn't stay
in the raccoon dog demon clan

37
00:04:04,310 --> 00:04:06,800
because you opposed
using the winged spirit pearl.

38
00:04:06,800 --> 00:04:07,520
So now

39
00:04:07,520 --> 00:04:10,120
you two wander around performing for a living.

40
00:04:11,080 --> 00:04:12,590
How miserable.

41
00:04:13,240 --> 00:04:13,840
This man is

42
00:04:13,840 --> 00:04:14,560
quite rich.

43
00:04:15,370 --> 00:04:16,280
Qiba,

44
00:04:16,280 --> 00:04:17,140
how about we...

45
00:04:18,750 --> 00:04:19,560
What?

46
00:04:20,240 --> 00:04:21,360
You want to kill me?

47
00:04:22,130 --> 00:04:24,910
[Quan Rumu, Young Master
of the Quan Family of the Borderlands]

48
00:04:29,510 --> 00:04:31,600
We d-didn't offend you, did we?

49
00:04:31,950 --> 00:04:32,310
Yeah.

50
00:04:32,390 --> 00:04:33,790
Wh-Why did you come to us?

51
00:04:34,120 --> 00:04:34,560
What do you want from us?

52
00:04:34,560 --> 00:04:35,160
Enough.

53
00:04:35,750 --> 00:04:37,550
I want you to do something for me.

54
00:04:38,680 --> 00:04:40,510
Help me find and follow this person,

55
00:04:40,510 --> 00:04:42,370
and report his whereabouts to me.

56
00:04:42,390 --> 00:04:43,250
Where to find me

57
00:04:43,360 --> 00:04:45,360
is also written clearly on the note.

58
00:04:48,600 --> 00:04:49,950
Th-Th-This job

59
00:04:50,240 --> 00:04:50,770
is not...

60
00:04:51,120 --> 00:04:51,720
not easy.

61
00:04:52,040 --> 00:04:52,270
Yeah.

62
00:04:52,270 --> 00:04:54,680
This will involve food and lodging...

63
00:04:54,680 --> 00:04:54,950
Th-Th-This job

64
00:04:54,950 --> 00:04:56,190
is going to cost a lot of money.

65
00:04:56,190 --> 00:04:57,159
It's not an easy task.

66
00:04:57,159 --> 00:04:57,750
Enough.

67
00:04:58,070 --> 00:04:59,000
Don't be cheeky.

68
00:04:59,510 --> 00:05:00,640
How much do you want?

69
00:05:03,750 --> 00:05:05,280
Fi-Fi-Five hundred taels!

70
00:05:05,430 --> 00:05:06,000
Yeah.

71
00:05:07,310 --> 00:05:08,440
Five hundred taels?

72
00:05:10,390 --> 00:05:11,720
Forget about 500 taelsâ€”

73
