I don't even have five taels.

74
00:05:15,480 --> 00:05:16,310
Are you kidding us?

75
00:05:16,310 --> 00:05:17,800
When you raccoon dog demons court mates,

76
00:05:17,800 --> 00:05:18,190
you rely on

77
00:05:18,190 --> 00:05:20,040
