after transforming into human form, right?

78
00:05:20,040 --> 00:05:20,900
Growing a braid

79
00:05:21,040 --> 00:05:22,680
takes a very, very long time.

80
00:05:23,560 --> 00:05:24,420
And without it,

81
00:05:24,600 --> 00:05:25,630
