83
00:05:27,120 --> 00:05:27,630
right?

84
00:05:29,480 --> 00:05:30,870
I'll kill you!

85
00:05:43,070 --> 00:05:44,040
My braid...

86
00:05:44,680 --> 00:05:45,480
I'll keep

87
00:05:45,480 --> 00:05:46,810
your braid safe for you.

88
00:05:46,920 --> 00:05:48,720
Come to me after the task is done.

89
00:05:48,720 --> 00:05:50,159
I'll definitely help you reattach it

90
00:05:50,159 --> 00:05:51,000
perfectly.

91
00:05:54,310 --> 00:05:55,770
You shameless bastard...

92
00:05:55,950 --> 00:05:56,560
Qiba!

93
00:05:57,510 --> 00:05:58,000
Boss!

94
00:05:58,000 --> 00:05:58,560
Boss!

95
00:06:07,240 --> 00:06:08,310
Young Master Fugui,

96
00:06:08,310 --> 00:06:10,440
I've never seen such a big lake before.

97
00:06:10,920 --> 00:06:12,000
When spring comes next year,

98
00:06:12,000 --> 00:06:13,560
this place will surely be
even more beautiful.

99
00:06:13,560 --> 00:06:14,270
By then,

100
00:06:14,480 --> 00:06:16,740
