101
00:06:23,720 --> 00:06:24,850
Young Master Fugui.

102
00:06:25,630 --> 00:06:26,630
Don't worry.

103
00:06:27,600 --> 00:06:29,130
I know how to weave brocade.

104
00:06:29,750 --> 00:06:30,630
By that time,

105
00:06:30,870 --> 00:06:32,680
I'll weave this entire scene
into a brocade.

106
00:06:32,680 --> 00:06:33,750
When your eyes heal,

107
00:06:33,750 --> 00:06:35,010
I'll show it all to you.

108
