127
00:07:38,120 --> 00:07:40,180
Try to meet as few people as possible.

128
00:07:40,190 --> 00:07:40,520
Okay.

129
00:07:41,720 --> 00:07:42,510
But...

130
00:07:43,950 --> 00:07:45,080
Young Master Fugui,

131
00:07:45,270 --> 00:07:46,600
Chief Hongye

132
00:07:46,920 --> 00:07:48,720
should already be inside by now.

133
00:07:49,270 --> 00:07:50,560
If he finds out...

134
00:07:52,870 --> 00:07:53,630
If he finds out

135
00:07:53,630 --> 00:07:55,090
you can't see right now...

136
00:07:55,480 --> 00:07:56,740
As long as I don't lose,

137
00:07:57,040 --> 00:07:58,190
he won't care

138
00:07:58,510 --> 00:07:59,840
