Fugui was injured by a snake demon.

143
00:08:45,320 --> 00:08:46,520
He'll heal in a month.

144
00:08:47,480 --> 00:08:49,010
Since his eyes are injured,

145
00:08:49,549 --> 00:08:51,150
this Blue Sky Convention...

146
00:08:57,850 --> 00:09:01,780
[Li Muhai, Young Master of
the Li Family of Peach Garden]

147
00:09:01,840 --> 00:09:02,770
Fellow Daoists,

148
00:09:02,960 --> 00:09:04,600
the Blue Sky Convention is
a grand ceremony

149
00:09:04,600 --> 00:09:06,840
held once every 36 years
by our Yiqi Alliance.

150
00:09:06,840 --> 00:09:07,200
Today, our Li family

151
00:09:07,200 --> 00:09:08,720
acts as host.

152
00:09:08,960 --> 00:09:10,390
We hope to help the alliance

153
00:09:10,390 --> 00:09:12,630
select outstanding members
of the next generation.

154
00:09:12,630 --> 00:09:14,000
This Blue Sky Convention

155
00:09:14,000 --> 00:09:16,390
still follows
the Yiqi Alliance's tradition.

156
00:09:16,390 --> 00:09:17,080
The competition is divided into

157
00:09:17,080 --> 00:09:17,810
three parts:

158
00:09:17,970 --> 00:09:18,790
Physical Combat,

159
00:09:18,790 --> 00:09:19,270
Skill,

160
00:09:19,510 --> 00:09:20,270
and Mind,

161
00:09:20,600 --> 00:09:21,790
one part each day.

162
00:09:21,960 --> 00:09:23,200
This convention has brought together

163
00:09:23,200 --> 00:09:24,910
talented young people from
various families of the Yiqi Alliance...

164
00:09:24,910 --> 00:09:26,360
Master, we've found
the Young Master's whereabouts.

165
00:09:26,360 --> 00:09:27,720
After the prescribed competitions,

166
00:09:27,720 --> 00:09:28,870
those who excel will be chosen

167
00:09:28,870 --> 00:09:30,480
to observe the secret Spiritual Stone left

168
00:09:30,480 --> 00:09:32,270
by the Third Young Master of Aolai.

169
00:09:32,270 --> 00:09:33,960
Through the Spiritual Stone,

170
00:09:33,960 --> 00:09:35,120
those exceptionally gifted young people
may glimpse

171
00:09:35,120 --> 00:09:36,840
the message left
by the Third Young Master.

172
00:09:36,840 --> 00:09:39,240
At the same time, the Yiqi Alliance will

173
00:09:39,240 --> 00:09:41,480
carefully guide them
to become pillars of the alliance.

174
00:09:41,480 --> 00:09:42,960
You all know the rules now.

175
00:09:43,150 --> 00:09:45,080
Today is the first day of the competition:

176
00:09:45,080 --> 00:09:46,740
the Physical Combat Contest.

177
00:09:54,480 --> 00:09:55,270
Rumu!

178
00:09:57,150 --> 00:09:58,600
It's so difficult for me

179
00:09:59,600 --> 00:10:00,730
to see you even once.

180
00:10:18,720 --> 00:10:19,510
Father,

181
00:10:19,840 --> 00:10:21,370
what are you talking about?

182
00:10:22,000 --> 00:10:23,840
I was just heading to
the Blue Sky Convention.

183
00:10:23,840 --> 00:10:26,030
Then why didn't you go there with me?

184
00:10:27,870 --> 00:10:28,270
Well,

185
00:10:28,750 --> 00:10:31,240
of all the vast lands beneath the sky,

186
00:10:31,510 --> 00:10:32,750
the dullest place of all

187
00:10:32,750 --> 00:10:34,270
is by your side, Father.

188
00:10:39,120 --> 00:10:40,360
Your words

189
00:10:41,150 --> 00:10:43,110
are breaking my heart.

190
00:10:46,200 --> 00:10:48,120
My beloved father, you never do anything
for nothing.

191
00:10:48,120 --> 00:10:48,720
Tell me,

192
00:10:49,270 --> 00:10:50,930
you came specially to find meâ€”

193
00:10:51,080 --> 00:10:52,410
what do you want me to do?

194
00:10:55,440 --> 00:10:56,970
These friends of mine think

195
00:10:57,320 --> 00:10:59,850
that even though the Soldier is blind
for now,

196
00:10:59,960 --> 00:11:01,290
he's still invincible.

197
00:11:01,670 --> 00:11:02,910
So they want to see

198
00:11:02,910 --> 00:11:04,390
your true strength.

199
00:11:11,720 --> 00:11:13,580
The Soldier of Wangquan Manor...

200
00:11:16,080 --> 00:11:17,390
Wangquan Fugui.

201
00:11:18,150 --> 00:11:21,750
He shall challenge all of today's victors
in the Combat Contest.

202
00:11:22,080 --> 00:11:23,480
This is a battle of honor.

203
00:11:23,630 --> 00:11:24,320
The results

204
00:11:24,550 --> 00:11:27,410
will not affect your advancement
to the next round.

205
00:11:28,240 --> 00:11:29,720
Good luck, everyone.

206
00:11:30,720 --> 00:11:31,600
Everyone,

207
00:11:31,840 --> 00:11:33,240
please draw your swords!

208
00:13:05,320 --> 00:13:06,000
Rumu.

209
00:13:07,790 --> 00:13:09,050
You're in poor health.

210
00:13:10,270 --> 00:13:13,030
After that strike, you won't be able
to exert any more strength.

211
00:13:13,030 --> 00:13:14,750
Go back with me.

212
00:13:23,840 --> 00:13:25,240
You are my son.

213
00:13:26,550 --> 00:13:28,670
Why can't you just listen to me

214
00:13:28,670 --> 00:13:30,150
and follow my will?

215
00:13:31,000 --> 00:13:32,360
Would I harm you?

216
00:13:32,790 --> 00:13:35,240
Everything I do and everything I getâ€”

217
00:13:36,200 --> 00:13:38,130
won't it all be yours in the future?

218
00:13:40,480 --> 00:13:41,150
Father...

219
00:13:42,480 --> 00:13:44,030
So it turns out you love me.

220
00:13:45,630 --> 00:13:46,360
Fine.

221
00:13:46,910 --> 00:13:48,320
How about I tell you

222
00:13:48,550 --> 00:13:49,910
some stories about

223
00:13:50,630 --> 00:13:52,430
how you, my real father, love me?

224
00:13:55,790 --> 00:13:56,480
Back then,

225
00:13:57,270 --> 00:13:58,510
you committed a grave error

226
00:13:58,510 --> 00:14:00,240
by practicing forbidden arts.

227
00:14:00,960 --> 00:14:02,910
You were expelled from Wangquan Manor

228
00:14:02,910 --> 00:14:04,840
and exiled to the Western Regions.

229
00:14:05,870 --> 00:14:07,750
You knew full well that I had asthma

230
00:14:07,750 --> 00:14:08,910
and that in that place

231
00:14:08,910 --> 00:14:10,440
I simply couldn't survive.

232
00:14:11,870 --> 00:14:13,530
The Chief intended to keep me,

233
00:14:13,720 --> 00:14:14,650
but at that time,

234
00:14:15,320 --> 00:14:16,440
what did you say?

235
00:14:21,480 --> 00:14:22,870
Rumu's asthma is severe.

236
00:14:22,740 --> 00:14:25,140
[Young Quan Rumu]

237
00:14:23,720 --> 00:14:25,210
If he goes with you
to the Western Regions,

238
00:14:25,210 --> 00:14:29,770
[Grand Ambition Soaring to the Heavens]

239
00:14:25,360 --> 00:14:26,890
with all that dust and sand,

240
00:14:27,870 --> 00:14:29,470
I'm afraid he won't survive.

241
00:14:30,270 --> 00:14:31,240
Let him stay.

242
00:14:32,030 --> 00:14:32,790
No need.

243
00:14:33,720 --> 00:14:34,520
Wherever I go,

244
00:14:34,870 --> 00:14:35,510
he goes.

245
00:14:41,270 --> 00:14:41,910
Jingting.

246
00:14:43,600 --> 00:14:44,800
If Rumu goes with you,

247
00:14:45,670 --> 00:14:46,670
he will die.

248
00:14:50,360 --> 00:14:52,270
I won't leave him here with you.

249
00:14:52,870 --> 00:14:54,630
Since he's my son,

250
00:14:55,000 --> 00:14:56,120
in life he's mine,

251
00:14:56,600 --> 00:14:58,460
and in death his ghost is mine too.

252
00:15:22,200 --> 00:15:23,060
Just like that,

253
00:15:24,030 --> 00:15:26,120
after we arrived in the Western Regions,

254
00:15:26,120 --> 00:15:27,790
my asthma grew increasingly severe.

255
00:15:27,790 --> 00:15:29,520
Even surviving was hard for me.

256
00:15:30,750 --> 00:15:31,440
And you?

257
00:15:32,200 --> 00:15:33,840
You began to ignore me,

258
00:15:34,030 --> 00:15:35,030
killing demons everywhere

259
00:15:35,030 --> 00:15:36,160
and making enemies.

260
00:15:47,750 --> 00:15:48,870
Finally, one day,

261
00:15:49,200 --> 00:15:51,730
someone captured me
as a hostage for revenge.

262
00:15:52,440 --> 00:15:53,630
At that time, I knew

263
00:15:54,360 --> 00:15:56,360
that taking me hostage was useless.

264
00:15:57,240 --> 00:15:58,480
My life meant nothing

265
00:15:58,750 --> 00:15:59,910
to you.

266
00:16:01,030 --> 00:16:02,390
But what you did

267
00:16:03,120 --> 00:16:05,240
was even worse than I imagined.

268
00:16:05,480 --> 00:16:06,340
Quan Jingting!

269
00:16:07,080 --> 00:16:08,600
I have your son!

270
00:16:09,150 --> 00:16:10,880
Give me back my mother's bones!

271
00:16:11,440 --> 00:16:13,770
That piece of trash is
of no use to me at all.

272
00:16:14,150 --> 00:16:15,360
Kill him if you want!

273
00:16:16,120 --> 00:16:16,870
Today...

274
00:16:17,870 --> 00:16:19,480
I'm here to capture you!

275
00:16:30,790 --> 00:16:31,750
After that,

276
00:16:32,390 --> 00:16:35,050
I wandered through the desert
for over 10 years.

277
00:16:37,440 --> 00:16:39,300
Did you ever look for me even once?

278
00:16:40,390 --> 00:16:41,150
You didn't.

279
00:16:42,600 --> 00:16:44,960
Did you care whether I lived or died?

280
00:16:45,360 --> 00:16:46,840
You didn't.

281
00:16:47,480 --> 00:16:50,120
But ever since I became famous
with one sword strike there,

282
00:16:50,120 --> 00:16:51,080
you remembered

283
00:16:51,080 --> 00:16:52,540
you still had a son like me.

284
00:16:52,790 --> 00:16:54,250
You remembered to love me.

285
00:16:54,480 --> 00:16:56,240
But how did you show this love?

