00:16:56,840 --> 00:16:58,500
For the sake of your ambition,

287
00:16:58,600 --> 00:17:00,330
you took my friends as hostages

288
00:17:00,960 --> 00:17:02,720
and forced me to work for you.

289
00:17:05,550 --> 00:17:06,240
Father,

290
00:17:07,150 --> 00:17:08,240
your love is

291
00:17:08,750 --> 00:17:10,630
more poisonous than arsenic.

292
00:17:10,790 --> 00:17:11,520
How dare you!

293
00:17:16,680 --> 00:17:18,310
You have such strength

294
00:17:19,480 --> 00:17:21,210
yet possess no grand ambition!

295
00:17:22,680 --> 00:17:24,940
I've been working hard for so many years.

296
00:17:25,790 --> 00:17:27,230
You are my son.

297
00:17:28,200 --> 00:17:29,790
You should work for me.

298
00:17:31,680 --> 00:17:33,480
Where have you imprisoned them?

299
00:17:37,589 --> 00:17:38,400
Rest assured,

300
00:17:39,000 --> 00:17:40,730
your gang of worthless friends

301
00:17:41,000 --> 00:17:42,310
is very safe now.

302
00:17:43,150 --> 00:17:44,720
As long as you obediently

303
00:17:44,720 --> 00:17:47,590
go to the Blue Sky Convention
and defeat the Soldier,

304
00:17:47,590 --> 00:17:49,070
I'll let them go.

305
00:17:50,110 --> 00:17:50,830
However...

306
00:18:00,680 --> 00:18:01,640
before that...

307
00:18:10,160 --> 00:18:11,790
you have to take this first.

308
00:18:15,480 --> 00:18:16,550
In this world,

309
00:18:17,830 --> 00:18:20,550
what kind of father
would ask his son to take this?

310
00:18:20,550 --> 00:18:21,350
This is just a pill

311
00:18:21,350 --> 00:18:24,030
that can greatly boost
your spiritual power.

312
00:18:24,880 --> 00:18:26,400
I want to ensure you win.

313
00:18:28,880 --> 00:18:30,210
Even if I don't eat it...

314
00:18:31,480 --> 00:18:33,210
I can still defeat the Soldier.

315
00:18:37,440 --> 00:18:39,510
You think I'd believe you?

316
00:18:40,480 --> 00:18:42,830
If I weren't holding the lives
of your worthless friends

317
00:18:42,830 --> 00:18:45,350
you made in the Western Regions,

318
00:18:45,790 --> 00:18:49,450
would you have obediently come with me
to the Blue Sky Convention?

319
00:18:49,880 --> 00:18:52,480
I know you've been looking for them
these days.

320
00:18:52,550 --> 00:18:53,400
Stop looking.

321
00:18:54,030 --> 00:18:56,030
Even if you find them, it's useless.

322
00:18:58,440 --> 00:18:59,370
What do you mean?

323
00:19:15,880 --> 00:19:17,440
Do you know what that black liquid

324
00:19:17,440 --> 00:19:18,680
is?

325
00:19:20,200 --> 00:19:21,000
Crude oil.

326
00:19:22,270 --> 00:19:23,590
With just a spark,

327
00:19:24,110 --> 00:19:25,970
these worthless friends of yours

328
00:19:26,680 --> 00:19:28,510
will be burned to ashes.

329
00:19:28,510 --> 00:19:29,510
Let us go.

330
00:19:30,070 --> 00:19:30,960
What do you want?

331
00:19:30,960 --> 00:19:31,890
Don't come over!

332
00:19:32,000 --> 00:19:32,930
Don't come over!

333
00:19:34,000 --> 00:19:34,790
Mother!

334
00:19:35,030 --> 00:19:35,960
What do you want?

335
00:19:38,480 --> 00:19:39,480
Don't come any closer!

336
00:19:39,480 --> 00:19:40,270
Let us go!

337
00:19:41,920 --> 00:19:42,720
No!

338
00:19:44,590 --> 00:19:45,200
No!

339
00:19:45,720 --> 00:19:46,510
Father!

340
00:19:46,510 --> 00:19:47,830
Mother!

341
00:19:48,160 --> 00:19:49,000
No!

342
00:20:08,110 --> 00:20:09,170
True Dragon Power?

343
00:20:10,270 --> 00:20:11,310
You wretch,

344
00:20:11,920 --> 00:20:14,650
say goodbye
to these worthless friends of yours.

345
00:20:15,200 --> 00:20:15,920
Wait!

346
00:20:18,920 --> 00:20:19,580
I'll eat it.

347
00:21:04,440 --> 00:21:06,720
Now that's my good boy.

348
00:21:08,640 --> 00:21:10,880
Today's Combat Contest is already over.

349
00:21:10,880 --> 00:21:12,720
The evening banquet will start soon.

350
00:21:12,720 --> 00:21:13,550
Go attend

351
00:21:14,030 --> 00:21:14,880
and make up for

352
00:21:15,680 --> 00:21:18,680
your willful absence earlier.

353
00:21:30,680 --> 00:21:32,960
This is the chamber
specially prepared for you, Soldier.

354
00:21:32,960 --> 00:21:34,240
There's also a side chamber inside

355
00:21:34,240 --> 00:21:35,830
for your maid.

356
00:21:36,400 --> 00:21:37,000
Thank you.

357
00:21:43,830 --> 00:21:44,960
Young Master Fugui,

358
00:21:45,070 --> 00:21:46,720
you must be very tired
from today's martial arts contest.

359
00:21:46,720 --> 00:21:47,750
Rest for a bit.

360
00:21:47,750 --> 00:21:49,750
You still have the banquet
to attend tonight.

361
00:21:49,750 --> 00:21:50,200
Okay.

362
00:22:09,510 --> 00:22:09,960
Come on.

363
00:22:09,960 --> 00:22:10,480
To you.

364
00:22:26,030 --> 00:22:27,750
This year's young competitors

365
00:22:27,750 --> 00:22:28,590
are very good.

366
00:22:29,270 --> 00:22:29,960
Hongye,

367
00:22:30,350 --> 00:22:32,440
indeed, they're good.

368
00:22:32,750 --> 00:22:34,400
But compared to us back in our day,

369
00:22:34,400 --> 00:22:36,130
they still fall a little short.

370
00:22:43,750 --> 00:22:44,350
Muhai,

371
00:22:44,680 --> 00:22:45,940
let the banquet begin.

372
00:22:46,790 --> 00:22:47,480
Everyone!

373
00:22:48,830 --> 00:22:50,350
Didn't you say

374
00:22:50,640 --> 00:22:52,900
you're hosting honored guests tonight?

375
00:22:53,110 --> 00:22:53,920
Then why...

376
00:22:54,590 --> 00:22:55,850
is there no seat for me?

377
00:22:59,880 --> 00:23:00,810
Who might you be?

378
00:23:01,550 --> 00:23:02,750
Good evening, Uncle.

379
00:23:03,310 --> 00:23:05,270
I, Rumu, missed today's competition,

380
00:23:05,270 --> 00:23:06,440
so I've come specially to ask you

381
00:23:06,440 --> 00:23:09,370
for the qualification
for tomorrow's competition.

382
00:23:21,640 --> 00:23:24,700
The Blue Sky Convention aims to
select future talents.

383
00:23:24,750 --> 00:23:26,160
If you want to participate,

384
00:23:26,160 --> 00:23:27,160
just ask them.

385
00:23:31,480 --> 00:23:32,160
Everyone!

386
00:23:33,440 --> 00:23:34,720
I'm Quan Rumu.

387
00:23:35,030 --> 00:23:36,630
I've come a long way for this.

388
00:23:36,830 --> 00:23:37,640
Please

389
00:23:38,070 --> 00:23:38,920
do me a favor.

390
00:23:41,550 --> 00:23:43,430
Today's banquet is only for

391
00:23:43,720 --> 00:23:46,240
the winners of today's Combat Contest.

392
00:23:46,720 --> 00:23:49,250
They have earned
the Soldier's recognition.

393
00:23:49,590 --> 00:23:51,790
Rumu, you were absent today.

394
00:23:52,030 --> 00:23:54,510
If the Chief allows it outright,

395
00:23:55,590 --> 00:23:57,030
it would be unfair.

396
00:23:57,750 --> 00:23:58,790
That's right.

397
00:24:02,750 --> 00:24:03,480
Rumu.

398
00:24:05,880 --> 00:24:07,810
Elder Shouyi is highly respected.

399
00:24:08,310 --> 00:24:10,910
You have to prove yourself
with your strength.

400
00:24:13,920 --> 00:24:14,750
I see.

401
00:24:15,400 --> 00:24:16,000
Okay.

402
00:24:17,000 --> 00:24:18,660
Then I'll trouble the Soldier

403
00:24:19,160 --> 00:24:20,420
to come out for a fight.

404
00:24:38,790 --> 00:24:40,190
Invite the Soldier over.

405
00:24:43,590 --> 00:24:44,400
Tonight,

406
00:24:44,680 --> 00:24:46,610
if you win the Soldier's approval,

407
00:24:47,270 --> 00:24:48,730
you may compete tomorrow.

408
00:25:03,270 --> 00:25:04,000
Cousin.

409
00:25:05,590 --> 00:25:06,790
It's been a long time.

410
00:25:07,680 --> 00:25:09,480
Why are you wearing a blindfold?

411
00:25:09,880 --> 00:25:10,750
Are you blind?

412
00:25:11,240 --> 00:25:12,370
Just a minor injury.

413
00:25:13,000 --> 00:25:14,000
Nothing serious.

414
00:26:09,610 --> 00:26:11,340
[Auspice from the East]

415
00:26:23,270 --> 00:26:24,930
See you at the arena tomorrow.

416
00:26:27,110 --> 00:26:27,920
Okay.

417
00:26:31,960 --> 00:26:32,920
Young people are

418
00:26:33,240 --> 00:26:35,170
indeed hot-blooded and vigorous.

419
00:26:35,830 --> 00:26:37,160
Just a small interlude.

420
00:26:37,510 --> 00:26:39,110
Let's continue our banquet.

421
00:26:43,830 --> 00:26:44,510
Cheers.

422
00:27:17,350 --> 00:27:18,480
Who are you?

423
00:27:19,110 --> 00:27:20,830
Judging from your swordsmanship,

424
00:27:20,830 --> 00:27:21,680
miss, you're

425
00:27:22,030 --> 00:27:24,200
a third-rate martial artist
in the alliance.

426
00:27:24,200 --> 00:27:24,590
Miss,

427
00:27:25,790 --> 00:27:27,790
how long have you been practicing
swordsmanship?

428
00:27:27,790 --> 00:27:30,250
What's your relationship with the Soldier?

429
00:27:31,960 --> 00:27:33,240
Why should I tell you?

430
00:27:34,110 --> 00:27:35,030
You haven't practiced your swordsmanship

431
00:27:35,030 --> 00:27:36,760
