432
00:27:37,480 --> 00:27:38,830
Your sword aura and inner breath

433
00:27:38,830 --> 00:27:40,430
are just like the Soldier's.

434
00:27:42,160 --> 00:27:43,150
I seem to...

435
00:27:44,000 --> 00:27:45,660
have discovered a big secret.

436
00:27:46,550 --> 00:27:47,010
What...

437
00:27:47,960 --> 00:27:49,030
What secret?

438
00:27:50,400 --> 00:27:51,550
You're not human.

439
00:27:54,030 --> 00:27:55,160
Who exactly are you?

440
00:28:06,110 --> 00:28:07,910
I can't sense your demonic aura.

441
00:28:08,310 --> 00:28:09,440
Why don't you tell me

442
00:28:09,830 --> 00:28:11,290
what kind of demon you are?

443
00:28:13,070 --> 00:28:13,550
Fine.

444
00:28:14,640 --> 00:28:15,440
I'll tell you.

445
00:28:16,640 --> 00:28:18,200
I'm not a demon.

446
00:28:25,270 --> 00:28:27,000
You're feistier than you look.

447
00:28:27,880 --> 00:28:28,960
You're not thinking of

448
00:28:28,960 --> 00:28:30,820
killing me to silence me, are you?

449
00:28:31,720 --> 00:28:32,160
Fine.

450
00:28:32,880 --> 00:28:34,540
I'll tell you another secret.

451
00:28:35,830 --> 00:28:37,070
I'm the one...

452
00:28:37,920 --> 00:28:39,720
who blinded the Soldier's eyes.

453
00:28:40,790 --> 00:28:41,240
You...

454
00:28:42,880 --> 00:28:44,350
You dare to hurt him?

455
00:28:45,110 --> 00:28:45,640
What?

456
00:28:46,200 --> 00:28:47,930
You're really going to kill me?

457
00:29:01,510 --> 00:29:02,440
No need to fight.

458
00:29:02,590 --> 00:29:03,590
He's not an enemy.

459
00:29:03,960 --> 00:29:05,220
Young Master Fugui...

460
00:29:07,000 --> 00:29:08,110
Aren't you blind?

461
00:29:08,200 --> 00:29:08,830
How do you know it's me?

462
00:29:08,830 --> 00:29:10,110
We crossed swords earlier.

463
00:29:10,110 --> 00:29:11,640
Naturally, I know it's you.

464
00:29:13,310 --> 00:29:14,350
Young Master Fugui,

465
00:29:14,350 --> 00:29:16,070
do you know what he just said to me?

466
00:29:16,070 --> 00:29:16,750
He said he's the one

467
00:29:16,750 --> 00:29:17,750
who blinded you.

468
00:29:18,590 --> 00:29:20,030
There's more to this matter.

469
00:29:20,030 --> 00:29:21,230
He is indeed a friend.

470
00:29:23,070 --> 00:29:23,960
In that case,

471
00:29:23,960 --> 00:29:25,620
it's all a misunderstanding.

472
00:29:26,680 --> 00:29:27,270
Fugui,

473
00:29:27,960 --> 00:29:29,550
your girl's swordsmanship is

474
00:29:29,550 --> 00:29:30,270
quite good.

475
00:29:37,000 --> 00:29:37,750
Hey.

476
00:29:38,750 --> 00:29:39,950
Don't talk nonsense.

477
00:29:41,350 --> 00:29:42,680
Such a strong reaction.

478
00:29:43,750 --> 00:29:44,830
You two

479
00:29:45,070 --> 00:29:47,470
haven't gotten to
that stage yet, have you?

480
00:29:53,960 --> 00:29:54,750
I...

481
00:29:55,350 --> 00:29:56,510
I'm just

482
00:29:56,510 --> 00:29:58,040
Young Master Fugui's maid.

483
00:29:58,640 --> 00:29:59,840
Don't talk nonsense.

484
00:30:00,160 --> 00:30:00,960
You should

485
00:30:01,790 --> 00:30:03,990
learn to speak like a normal person now.

486
00:30:04,680 --> 00:30:05,200
Then...

487
00:30:06,350 --> 00:30:07,160
what are

488
00:30:07,270 --> 00:30:08,640
the two of you, exactly?

489
00:30:09,000 --> 00:30:10,270
Mind your own business.

490
00:30:10,270 --> 00:30:11,270
How did things go?

491
00:30:11,880 --> 00:30:13,030
It's all done.

492
00:30:13,350 --> 00:30:14,270
I made an appointment with them

493
00:30:14,270 --> 00:30:15,680
to meet by the river tonight.

494
00:30:15,680 --> 00:30:16,740
Let's go there now.

495
00:30:17,110 --> 00:30:18,110
What do you think?

496
00:30:42,960 --> 00:30:43,470
What?

497
00:30:44,350 --> 00:30:45,280
It's not for you.

498
00:30:51,440 --> 00:30:52,720
You're the one who blinded

499
00:30:52,720 --> 00:30:53,750
Young Master Fugui.

500
00:30:53,750 --> 00:30:55,550
Who knows if you've poisoned it?

501
00:30:56,880 --> 00:30:58,340
Young Master Fugui, here.

502
00:30:58,550 --> 00:30:59,790
I already tried it.

503
00:30:59,790 --> 00:31:00,750
Just drink it.

504
00:31:05,920 --> 00:31:07,680
It's so cold even next to the bonfire.

505
00:31:07,680 --> 00:31:09,080
I'll go move around a bit.

506
00:31:22,000 --> 00:31:23,480
What are you doing?

507
00:31:25,830 --> 00:31:26,510
Fugui,

508
00:31:27,160 --> 00:31:28,220
let's have a round?

509
00:31:28,400 --> 00:31:30,600
Who are you pretending to be close with?

510
00:32:08,880 --> 00:32:10,010
Young Master Fugui!

511
00:32:10,310 --> 00:32:11,510
You're so amazing!

512
00:32:11,920 --> 00:32:12,720
How can that stone

513
00:32:12,720 --> 00:32:14,880
skip on the water for so long?

514
00:32:17,640 --> 00:32:18,840
Do you want to know...

515
00:32:19,640 --> 00:32:20,550
our story?

516
00:32:25,160 --> 00:32:26,720
The rumors outside are so exaggerated.

517
