[16 years ago, Cold Pool]

518
00:32:27,030 --> 00:32:27,880
What barrier?

519
00:32:28,510 --> 00:32:30,070
What "no outsiders" rule?

520
00:32:30,400 --> 00:32:31,440
How exaggerated.

