525
00:32:42,720 --> 00:32:44,920
Why don't they serve anything tastier?

526
00:32:46,350 --> 00:32:46,920
Ghost!

527
00:32:50,060 --> 00:32:53,600
[Young Wangquan Fugui]

528
00:32:50,480 --> 00:32:51,010
Soldier,

529
00:32:51,590 --> 00:32:52,790
why are you standing behind me

530
00:32:52,790 --> 00:32:54,120
without making a sound?

531
00:32:54,590 --> 00:32:55,790
Listening to sounds.

532
00:32:55,880 --> 00:32:57,080
Listening to sounds?

533
00:32:57,680 --> 00:32:59,140
You really aren't normal.

534
00:32:59,310 --> 00:33:00,240
Ignore me.

535
00:33:00,240 --> 00:33:01,370
I won't disturb you.

536
00:33:01,720 --> 00:33:03,510
I just came in to look for something.

537
00:33:03,510 --> 00:33:04,910
I'll leave once I find it.

538
00:33:05,590 --> 00:33:06,400
You are Rumu?

539
00:33:06,880 --> 00:33:07,640
Yes, yes.

540
00:33:07,960 --> 00:33:08,960
Your cousin.

541
00:33:09,200 --> 00:33:10,070
The one who spars with you

542
00:33:10,070 --> 00:33:12,310
and gets knocked down
the fastest every time.

543
00:33:12,310 --> 00:33:13,640
You did that on purpose.

544
00:33:16,920 --> 00:33:18,120
You saw through that?

545
00:33:18,830 --> 00:33:20,000
Why do those sparring partners

546
00:33:20,000 --> 00:33:21,200
take it so seriously?

547
00:33:21,440 --> 00:33:22,920
We're all going to
get knocked down anyway.

548
00:33:22,920 --> 00:33:24,780
Might as well fall early and rest.

549
00:33:38,110 --> 00:33:39,030
Here you are.

550
00:33:40,720 --> 00:33:41,750
It's my friend.

551
00:33:45,440 --> 00:33:47,070
Now you're being unreasonable.

552
00:33:47,070 --> 00:33:48,480
How is it your friend?

553
00:33:48,750 --> 00:33:50,030
It's my only friend.

554
00:33:50,960 --> 00:33:52,310
Keep this up, and I'll get angry.

555
00:33:52,310 --> 00:33:52,790
Get out.

556
00:33:53,270 --> 00:33:54,470
This is my courtyard!

557
00:33:54,640 --> 00:33:56,570
You really think I'm afraid of you?

558
00:34:09,720 --> 00:34:10,720
I'm sorry.

559
00:34:12,590 --> 00:34:14,190
It was really my only friend.

560
00:34:17,960 --> 00:34:18,640
Just now,

561
00:34:19,510 --> 00:34:21,639
you said you were listening to sounds.

562
00:34:22,000 --> 00:34:24,600
Were you listening to
the cricket's chirping?

563
00:34:24,840 --> 00:34:25,880
So, it was

564
00:34:26,110 --> 00:34:28,370
the only living thing here, besides you?

565
00:34:28,440 --> 00:34:29,190
It's...

566
00:34:29,670 --> 00:34:30,960
eerily quiet here.

567
00:34:32,320 --> 00:34:33,179
Being a Soldier

568
00:34:33,670 --> 00:34:35,000
is this miserable?

